headline: Regulatory Delays and Weakening Margins Weigh on Morgan Stanley’s ADM Outlook
summary: Archer-Daniels-Midland Company (NYSE:ADM) is included among the 12 Best Income Stocks to Buy Now. On December 16, Morgan Stanley analyst Steven Haynes downgraded Archer-Daniels-Midland Company (NYSE:ADM) to Underweight from Equal Weight and cut the price target to $50 from $57.
